wikipedia_page.main: Oliver Henry Moors (born 24 September 1996) is a British professional road and track cyclist, who currently rides for UCI Continental team Ribble Weldtite. He has won five national titles in his specialist discipline and has represented Great Britain at the 2016 and 2017 UEC European Derny Championships. Moors also previously rode for the professional American UCI Continental team, Astellas in 2016.
